The staff list for this show is insane- The director is Fuga Yamashiro a veteran of Science SARU this is his directorial debut, The character designer is Naoyuki Onda. He did character designs for Ergo Proxy  Rage of Bahamut and Gantz, The alien and creature designs are by the legendary Yoshimichi Kameda. Hes done way too much  but among his notable works includes - FMAB  Mob Psycho and One Punch Man. But heres the best part the majority of EP1 was key animated by young new animators  rather then veterans like Kameda. The sheer directorial and storyboard work of the episode director  Abel Gongora (another major member of Science SARU  worked on Scott Pilgrim, Devilman, etc.)  made it look this good.
